{"tid":1303740,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警治港 係香港民主嘅踏腳石","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:03:33.000Z","uid":81805,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45098a00b107844f0d0a7f327a65a874dfeb5aae","tid":1303740,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:03:31.000Z","msg":"唔該大家應清楚最重要嘅係乜嘢！條例撤回都可以再重啟！<br />\n<br />\n依家香港最重要嘅問題之一係黑警治港，黑警權力過大，無人監管，令到政府硬推嘅條例好容易通過，邊個上街反對就打鳩佢！<br />\n<br />\n香港人依家最大既訴求係 <br />\n<br />\n1. 追究黑警濫權，行為不當<br />\n2. 成立獨立調查小組調查黑警<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士，並承諾不追究<br />\n4. 立即啟動雙普選"},{"pid":"e44c54d4d0c3219576490b1637534f1cea12e977","tid":1303740,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"主力追究黑警"},{"pid":"7692e886bb3e41660be5adc16024e3c54a7a34a3","tid":1303740,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"黑警嘅問題大到好擔心"},{"pid":"40cf2c965bf7ebe46945713d0a8894fe04e80c7f","tid":1303740,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>NOW</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30</span></span><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ecb1213b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a hr